  <h1 class="title">2007 - Mobile Internet and the iPhone launch</h1>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>
          The year 2007 marked a pivotal moment in the evolution of mobile
          technology. Apple’s iPhone, launched in June 2007, revolutionized the
          way people interacted with the internet, bringing mobile internet
          access to the forefront of consumer technology. The iPhone was not
          just a phone - it was a powerful, compact computer that combined
          internet connectivity, a touch interface, and an app ecosystem,
          setting the stage for the mobile internet revolution in the UK and
          around the world.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
